building safe and supportive environments for nutrition at all ages; and
strengthening and promoting nutrition governance and accountability, everywhere.
WHO response
WHO aims for a world free of all forms of malnutrition, where all people achieve health and wellbeing. According to the 2016–2025 nutrition strategy, WHO works with Member States and partners towards universal access to effective nutrition interventions and to healthy diets from sustainable and resilient food systems.
